title: "Colored `ls` Output in OpenBSD"
tags:
  - openbsd
id: 506
categories:
  - Software
date: 2010-03-28 06:22:26
---

After `# pkg_add -iv fileutils` , in `$HOME/.profile`, include:
{% codeblock lang:bash %}
eval $(/usr/local/bin/gdircolors -b)
alias ls='/usr/local/bin/gls --color=always'
{% endcodeblock %}


